snippet.title: METAL GEAR RISING/MEGA64 E3 TRAILER
snippet.description:
Mega64 and Konami present their METAL GEAR RISING: REVENGEANCE E3 trailer. 

MGR:R early demo included in ZONE OF THE ENDERS HD COLLECTION to be released this holiday season! 

Playable at E3!

Check out the gameplay trailer here: http://youtu.be/2ONT6-8B94Y

http://metalgearsolid.com/rising/

http://mega64.com
